==English==
{{Wikipedia|Anastasi (disambiguation)| anastasi}}
===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

'''Object''': A traditional [[weapon]]/[[tool]] used by the [[prehistoric]] settlers in the Maltese Islands. The anastasi had a [[phallic]] resemblance. Theories about its use and [[utility]] are scarce, however, it is said that anastasis were used in the hunt for small game which abounded on the [[island]] at the time.